  <brief_title>Risk Factors for Incontinence-Associated Dermatitis (IAD) in ICU Patients Suffering From Fecal Incontinence</brief_title>
  <official_title>Specific Factors Associated With the Development of Incontinence- Associated Dermatitis (IAD) in ICU Patients Suffering From Fecal Incontinence: Matched Case Control Study</official_title>
